### Parser
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [RuleBasedParser.kt](file:///d:/second_brain/app/src/main/java/in/karthiknp/secondbrain/parser/RuleBasedParser.kt) | **Core NLP engine**: 6 regex patterns, keyword fallback, date/time extraction, query intent detection |

**Supported patterns:**
- `"Remind me to X at Y"` → TASK with datetime
- `"Todo: X"` / `"Task: X"` / `"Need to X"` → TASK
- `"Name birthday Month Day"` → EVENT (recurring)
- `"Birthday of Name on Date"` → EVENT
- `"Schedule: X at Y"` → EVENT
- `"Idea: X"` / `"Note: X"` → IDEA
- Keyword fallback for 20+ task and 14+ event keywords
- Query detection: `"Show my ideas"`, `"Upcoming birthdays"`, etc.

