## How to Build & Run

1. Open `d:\second_brain` in Android Studio
2. **Sync Gradle** (File → Sync Project with Gradle Files)
3. Wait for the sync to complete (first time may take a few minutes to download deps)
4. Connect a device or start an emulator (API 26+)
5. Click **Run ▶**

## Running Tests

In Android Studio terminal:
```
./gradlew test
```
Or right-click `RuleBasedParserTest.kt` → Run

